  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a cazuela over medium until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and paprika, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Sprinkle arrowroot powder over the mixture, stirring to prevent clumps.",
    "Pour vegetable broth and milk, bringing to a gentle simmer.",
    "Reduce heat and add grated Bryndza cheese, stirring until melted and the sauce is velvety.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper, adjusting to taste.",
    "Let the soup simmer for 5 minutes, allowing flavors to meld.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley before serving.",
    "Serve hot, optionally with a slice of gluten‑free bread on the side."
  ],
